high_descs: Go to the sink behind you.
Take the soap bar nearest to you.
Take the soap bar to the sink next to you.
Wash the soap bar in the sink.
Take the soap bar to the trash bin to your right.
Place the soap bar in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed soap bar in the trash.

high_descs: Pick up the soap in the back by the sink.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Put the soap in the middle of the sink, turn on the water, keeping the soap dry.
Pick up the soap and bring it to the trash can.
Put the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a soap in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and left, walk to the side of the vanity
Grab the pink sponge in the back
Turn left and walk to in between the two sinks
Put the pink sponge in between the two sinks, turn on the faucet on the left, turn off the faucet, take the sponge
Turn right, walk to the trash bin
Put the sponge in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Take the pink sponge near the mirror, wash it in the sink, put the sponge in the trash bin
